<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM13.5">
<l>aḻilun toḻilu murukkāṭṭā ṉañcē leṉṉā ṉavaṉoruvaṉ</l>
<l>taḻuvi muḻucip pukunteṉṉaic cuṟṟic cuḻaṉṟu pōkāṉāl</l>
<l>taḻaiyiṉ poḻilvāy niraippiṉṉē neṭumā lūti varukiṉṟa</l>
<l>kuḻaliṉ tuḷaivāy nīrkoṇṭu kuḷira mukattut taṭavīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who does not show Himself whether one cries or prays,</l>
<l rend="indent">He who does not say, ‘Do not fear!’</l>
<l>Entered [here], embraced and dived [into me], and [now] will not leave,</l>
<l rend="indent">embracing and whirling me around, alas!</l>
<l>Will you not bring water [that seeps] through the holes of the flute</l>
<l rend="indent">that the tall Māl comes blowing</l>
<l>[going] behind herds of cows in the flourishing groves and rub [it] on [my] face</l>
<l rend="indent">so that [that water] cools it?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
